---
---

<section class="px-6 py-section sm:py-section-lg bg-black text-white">
  <div class="section-container">
    <span class="section-eyebrow">CAPABILITIES</span>
    <h2 class="section-title text-center reveal">Core capabilities</h2>
    <div class="mt-14 grid gap-6 sm:gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="card-dark reveal">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white text-black flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Stay in the moment.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-ink-200 leading-relaxed">
          Ask without ever leaving the game. No alt-tab, no phone, no break in immersion.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-dark reveal" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white text-black flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20"/><path d="M2 12h20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">It knows where you are.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-ink-200 leading-relaxed">
          Reads your current quest, stage, location, and NPCs live — not guessed from a screenshot.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-dark reveal" style="transition-delay: 80ms;">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white text-black flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H20v20H6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0-5H20"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Trust what it tells you.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-ink-200 leading-relaxed">
          Grounded in real game wikis and guides, not made-up lore. What you hear is what's true.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-dark reveal" style="transition-delay: 160ms;">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-white text-black flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17.94 17.94A10.07 10.07 0 0 1 12 20c-7 0-11-8-11-8a18.45 18.45 0 0 1 5.06-5.94M9.9 4.24A9.12 9.12 0 0 1 12 4c7 0 11 8 11 8a18.5 18.5 0 0 1-2.16 3.19M14.12 14.12a3 3 0 1 1-4.24-4.24"/><line x1="1" y1="1" x2="23" y2="23"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">No spoilers, just where you are.</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-ink-200 leading-relaxed">
          It explains what's happening now without ruining what's next. You decide how much to know.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
